<item>
            <title>[PIG-3077] TestMultiQueryLocal should not write in /tmp</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3077</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;temporary files from tests should be under build/test so that they are cleaned by &quot;ant clean&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
Currently two test suites running on the same machine step on each other and create flaky tests results&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12618806">PIG-3077</key>
            <summary>TestMultiQueryLocal should not write in /tmp</summary>
