                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13601648" author="dreambird" created="Wed, 13 Mar 2013 21:13:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;this patch respect &apos;pig.temp.dir&apos; first in case we want to put temp file in other location. Otherwise set location as System.getProperty(&quot;user.dir&quot;) + &quot;/build/test/tmp/&quot;. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It uses the FileLocalizer to get temp dir from PigContext, and then replace all /tmp in the test code.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I verify it and TestMultiQueryLocal passes for me.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13601720" author="prkommireddi" created="Wed, 13 Mar 2013 22:00:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=dreambird&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;dreambird&quot;&gt;Johnny Zhang&lt;/a&gt;, thanks for working on this. I have a comment:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; tdir = &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;.getProperty(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;user.dir&quot;&lt;/span&gt;) + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/build/test/tmp/&quot;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;user.dir would not be required here. Setting tdir to &quot;build/test/tmp&quot; should work.&lt;/p&gt;

</comment>
                            <comment id="13602563" author="cheolsoo" created="Thu, 14 Mar 2013 18:47:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;To get the path without the scheme, you can do:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
FileLocalizer.getTemporaryPath(myPig.getPigContext()).toUri().getPath()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;instead of&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (TMP_DIR.startsWith(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;file:/&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)) {
   TMP_DIR = TMP_DIR.substring(5, TMP_DIR.length());
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13603024" author="dreambird" created="Fri, 15 Mar 2013 01:57:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=prkommireddi&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;prkommireddi&quot;&gt;Prashant Kommireddi&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=cheolsoo&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;cheolsoo&quot;&gt;Cheolsoo Park&lt;/a&gt;, thanks a lot for checking the code. I just post the new patch to resolve your comments.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13603152" author="cheolsoo" created="Fri, 15 Mar 2013 05:25:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1. I will commit it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13603155" author="cheolsoo" created="Fri, 15 Mar 2013 05:30:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed to trunk. Thanks Johnny!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
